    "title": "Pyramid Application",
    "prompt": "A candle is in the shape of a right pyramid with a square base that has an<br> area of 144 square inches. The slant height of the candle is 10 inches. <\/br>What is the total surface area of the candle?",
    "description": null,
    "hint": null,
